title: MisterMusic Show 343 - new indie,alternative,rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show 343 [120 minutes] 192kbps MP3



Several new songs make their way to The MisterMusic Show this week.
Tunes from Trust Fund, Siskiyou, Imagine Dragons, Lady Lamb the Beekeeper, and another song from the latest Noel Gallagher's High Flying Birds album. 
And, the 'Oldie of the Week' spent the entire month of February on top of the chart in 1982. A 70s era classic rock band finally scored a number 1 hit after 12 years of recording.

It's Indie, Alternative, and Rock from over 5 decades...The MisterMusic Show- broadcast weekly and heard globally on RockXS internet radio.
